                     <interp inst="t18370918-2260-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18370918-2260-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp> for feloniously receiving the same, well knowing them to have been Stolen; to which Cadwallader pleaded</rs>
