                     <interp inst="t18370918-2260-punishment-207" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2260-18370918 t18370918-2260-punishment-207"></join>Transported for Fourteen Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>(There were other indictments against the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>Before Mr. Justice Patteson.</p>
